1.16
log
@
update to subversion snapshot from 2008-06-20.

added since last update:

- AVM2 (Flash 9) SWF muxer
- QT variant of IMA ADPCM encoder
- VFW grabber
- Ipod/Iphone compatible mp4 muxer
- Mimic decoder
- MSN TCP Webcam stream demuxer
- RL2 demuxer / decoder
- IFF demuxer
- 8SVX audio decoder
- BFI demuxer
- MAXIS EA XA (.xa) demuxer / decoder
- BFI video decoder
- OMA demuxer

also:
* headers have been moved to library specific subdirectories instead
  of all under ffmpeg.
* libswscale is now enabled in the build.


feedback/ok brad@@
@
text
@$OpenBSD: patch-libavformat_Makefile,v 1.15 2008/01/26 01:56:02 jakemsr Exp $
